    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-11-02T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-11-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="90"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d90">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="#p_WJG1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Winant</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">President</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d90fn1">Sent to Washington by the United States Military
                        Attaché, London, and forwarded by the White House Map Room to <persName
                            corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> at Hyde Park.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-11-02">2 November
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Personal and secret to the President from <persName corresp="#p_WJG1"
                        >Winant</persName>.</p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                <p>1. If you travel I would like to meet with you. There would be no objection here
                    and my transportation could be easily arranged. Never <pb facs="0156" n="64"
                        xml:id="pg_64"/> attending conferences has put me outside the lines of
                    communications and has cut down my usefulness to you.</p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
            </div>
        </body>
